verbose_text: After 3 or 4 divisions, the more activated progenitor cell appears to give rise to an irreversibly determined effector cell with de novo silencing of TCF1 expression, alongside a self renewing progenitor cell, which is more anabolic and activated than a quiescent memory cell, but maintains TCF1 expression and the bipotency to yield daughter cells with discordant silencing of TCF1.
